snippet.title: NFL Rivals Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready to be the General Manager of your own NFL football team? Show off your pro sports manager skills in NFL Rivals, an officially licensed professional mobile football game with digital player cards.

Get ahead of the pack and be a part of one of the NFL’s biggest moves! Join the game now during Offseason to help shape the future of one of the hottest officially licensed NFL and NFLPA mobile games, and enjoy special 2023 NFL Draft Player Packs and themed in-game events. Unlock your favorite football pros, draft your star players, set your lineups, and gear up in your Squads. It’s time to get game-day ready.

Download free now: https://nflrivals.sng.link/D6fxh/z6gq/x94n
